issue.title: Added a visual cue for unsaved changes (issue 7)
issue.body:
## Purpose

To add a visual cue to indicate that changes to reminders have not been saved

## Approach

Added text reminders to each item that has dirty attributes

### Learning

Same as our revert issue, used ember docs for "hasDirtyAttributes"

### Test coverage 

Tested to see if the class of "unsaved" has a length of 1 after changes have been made and not saved

issue.title: Added revert test and functionality (issue 6)
issue.body:
Purpose

Added a "revert" button that is displayed if there are dirty attributes which will revert any changes made.

Approach

Utilized "hasDirtyAttributes" to determine whether to display the revert button.

Learning

https://guides.emberjs.com/v2.1.0/components/handling-events/
http://emberjs.com/api/data/classes/DS.Model.html#property_hasDirtyAttributes

Test coverage

Attempted to test whether the reminder reverted back to its original state
